    <h3>Compensation for Referrals</h3>
    <p>CompareWeightMeds participates in affiliate marketing programs. When you click on certain links to providers on our Site and subsequently sign up for their services, we may receive compensation in the form of commissions. This compensation comes at no additional cost to you.</p>
    
    <h3>Editorial Independence</h3>
    <p>Our affiliate relationships do not influence our reviews, scores, rankings, or editorial content. Providers cannot pay for better scores, higher rankings, or preferential treatment in our comparisons. Our proprietary TeleHealth Score methodology is applied consistently to all providers based on objective criteria, regardless of affiliate status.</p>
    
    <h3>Providers We Work With</h3>
    <p>We maintain affiliate relationships with several GLP-1 telehealth providers reviewed on this Site. We also review providers with whom we do not have affiliate relationships. The absence of an affiliate link does not indicate a negative review; it simply means we have not established a commercial relationship with that provider.</p>
    
    <h2>Accuracy of Information</h2>
    
