    <p>We are not responsible for errors, omissions, or changes in provider information. Always verify pricing, policies, and medication details directly with the provider before making a decision.</p>
    
    <h3>Third-Party Content</h3>
    <p>This Site may include customer reviews, ratings from third-party platforms (e.g., Trustpilot, Better Business Bureau), and links to external websites. We do not control, endorse, or assume responsibility for third-party content. Inclusion of third-party content does not imply endorsement.</p>
    
    <h2>User Responsibilities</h2>
    
    <h3>Use at Your Own Risk</h3>
    <p>Your use of this Site and reliance on any information provided is solely at your own risk. We expressly disclaim any liability for damages, losses, or adverse outcomes resulting from use of information found on this Site.</p>
    
    <h3>Do Your Own Research</h3>
    <p>This Site is a starting point for research, not an endpoint. Before choosing a GLP-1 telehealth provider or starting medication:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Consult with your primary care physician</li>
      <li>Research provider credentials and reviews independently</li>
      <li>Verify pricing and policies directly with the provider</li>
      <li>Read all terms, conditions, and refund policies carefully</li>
      <li>Ask questions and request clarification when needed</li>
    </ul>
    
